<p style="text-align: left;">Lastly, Angela and I would like to thank you all so much for your continued support this year. You all are honestly the most encouraging, uplifting, helpful, and FUN bunch. We&#8217;re so grateful to everyone and wish all of you happy holidays and a spectacularly successful New Year! We&#8217;ll see you all January 5th!</p>
